    "For the GPT-4 scores, we also have written justifications for the first round of predicted scores.",
    "As the first step, we contrasted the average OP and OSV scores per occupation from the survey with the GPT-4 generated scores.",
    "GPT-4 scores (averaged across 50 iterations) range from 0 to 87.8.",
    "Across all 580 occupations, the OP arithmetic mean is 54.1, which is somewhat higher than the survey responses, where the global OP average was 45.9.",
